The raspberry pi runs Raspbian Stretch with ROS Kinetic. Installation procedure is available at-
https://www.raspberrypi.org/documentation/installation/installing-images/
http://wiki.ros.org/ROSberryPi/Installing%20ROS%20Kinetic%20on%20the%20Raspberry%20Pi

The image for Raspbian Stretch is available at-
https://downloads.raspberrypi.org/raspbian/images/raspbian-2019-04-09/

The agent uses Mavros for remote operation. It can be installed by following- 
https://github.com/mavlink/mavros
